    "adi": {
      "author": "Swami Adidevananda",
      "et":
          "10.35 Of Saman hymns, I am the Brhatsaman. Of meters, I am the Gayatri. Of months, I am Margasira (Nov-Dec). And of seasons I am the season of flowers."
